g.text: Level 3 FE Diagram for Create Staff
Sends HTTP Request to get all Specializations
Intercepts the request and adds the token to the header
The token is added to the header so that the MDR
can authenticate and authorize the request.
Sends HTTP Request to get staff types
Intercepts the request and adds the token to the header
The token is added to the header so that the MDR
can authenticate and authorize the request.
Tries to get Staffs Types data
Sends Staff's data (FirstName, LastName, FullName, Email, PhoneNumber, StaffType, SpecializationName)
Sends HTTP Request to create a Staff with Staff's data
Intercepts the request and adds the token to the header
The token is added to the header so that the MDR
can authenticate and authorize the request.
Sends HTTP Request with token to create a Staff
Validates Staff's data and tries to create the Staff
